      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for your next adventure. While it shows some light signs of regular use, it drives beautifully and offers a comfortable, solid experience behind the wheel. It's a great opportunity to own a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to go!",
