    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. This vehicle is in showroom condition, featuring flawless original paint with a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional multi-stage ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface operates with the tactile precision of a vehicle that just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records. It has recently undergone a full fluid service and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it drives as flawlessly as it looks. Included are both original keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 47900.0,
